Package eu.opends.environment.vegetation

Class RoadSideVegetation

java.lang.Object
eu.opends.environment.vegetation.RoadSideVegetation
public class RoadSideVegetation
extends java.lang.Object
Road side vegetation is a collection of 3D models (e.g. trees, bushes, etc.) placed along a single OpenDRIVE road. Several parameters (like side of road, distance between two objects, distance from road reference line, start/end position) can be provided.
Author:
Rafael Math
